OL,6,FEbid even told an associate to kill
OL,7,Fand throw into the sea any migrants
OL,8,Fcaught with phones, in a bid to avoid
OL,9,Flaw enforcement, the NCA said ` all
OL,10,Fwhile he was living in Isleworth.
OL,12,FHe was living on benefits in a
OL,13,Ftaxpayer-funded home, having arrived
OL,14,Fin the country as an asylum seeker in
OL,15,F2022, according to reports, despite a
OL,16,Fprevious drug-smuggling conviction in
OL,17,FItaly.
