OL,6,FHe added that the "truly staggering"
OL,7,Famount of money came from the "hard-
OL,8,Fearned savings of desperate
OL,9,Findividuals", who were "ruthlessly and
OL,10,Fcynically exploited" by Ebid and the
OL,11,Fcrime group.
OL,13,FThe judge said "exploitation on such
OL,14,Fan enormous scale" causes "so much
OL,15,Fmisery" and "could so easily lead to a
OL,16,Fconsiderable loss of life".
OL,18,FThe judge also said: "The treatment of
OL,19,Fthe migrants on your orders and in
OL,20,Fyour name was horrifying. They were
OL,21,Fsimply a commodity to you.
