OL,6,F"You talked of them in terms of units,
OL,7,Fnot as people, referring to them as
OL,8,F'cartons'.
OL,10,F"The important thing to you was that
OL,11,Feach paid up the exorbitant fare that
OL,12,Fwas charged for their crossing and
OL,13,Fthat nobody did anything to compromise
OL,14,Fyour operation ` such as by carrying a
OL,15,Fmobile phone.
