OL,6,F"As we know, if they did, you were
OL,7,Fprepared to instruct others to
OL,8,Fthreaten them with death. You
OL,9,Fdemonstrated no empathy or care
OL,10,Fwhatsoever for these desperate and
OL,11,Fvulnerable men, women and children. "
OL,13,FHe added: "There has to be, it seems
OL,14,Fto me, a crystal-clear message
OL,15,Fdelivered to those engaged in this
OL,16,Ftrade, that the protection of
OL,17,Finternational borders is also
OL,18,Fsomething that, when the court has
OL,19,Fsuch a responsibility, is taken very
OL,20,Fseriously indeed and reflected in a
OL,21,Flengthy sentence being passed."
