OL,6,FThe defendant was heard ranting in the
OL,7,Fdock after the sentencing, while a
OL,8,Fwoman in the public gallery wept.
OL,10,FEbid arrived in the UK in October 2022
OL,11,Fafter crossing the Channel in a small
OL,12,Fboat, having been sentenced in Italy
OL,13,Fin 2017 to a total of six years and
OL,14,Ftwo months in prison for drug-
OL,15,Fsmuggling.
OL,17,FSoon afterwards, he began arranging
OL,18,Fthe operations in the Mediterranean.
