OL,6,FHe was working with people-smuggling
OL,7,Fnetworks to organise boats, bringing
OL,8,Fover hundreds of migrants at a time on
OL,9,Fextremely dangerous vessels from Libya
OL,10,Fand advertising the crossings on
OL,11,FFacebook.
OL,13,FEbid sourced and provided boats and
OL,14,Fcrews, provided technical advice
OL,15,Fduring the crossings, helped house
OL,16,Fmigrants, and dealt with any required
OL,17,Fpaperwork, prosecutors said.
