OL,6,FIn one conversation with an associate,
OL,7,Frecorded via a listening device
OL,8,Fplanted by NCA officers, he said
OL,9,Fmigrants were not to carry phones with
OL,10,Fthem on his boats.
OL,12,FHe said: "Tell them guys anyone caught
OL,13,Fwith a phone will be killed, threw in
OL,14,Fthe sea."
OL,16,FOne crossing on October 25 2022 saw
OL,17,Fmore than 640 migrants rescued by the
OL,18,FItalian authorities after they
OL,19,Fattempted to cross in a wooden boat,
OL,20,Fthe NCA said.
