OL,6,FIt was taken into port in Sicily and
OL,7,Ftwo bodies were recovered.
OL,9,FIn another, 265 migrants were rescued
OL,10,Fby the Italian coastguard from a 20m
OL,11,F(66ft) fishing boat found adrift in
OL,12,Fthe Mediterranean in early December
OL,13,F2022 after it left Benghazi.
OL,15,FTwo search and rescue operations
OL,16,Foccurred in April 2023 after distress
OL,17,Fcalls to the coastguard and in each
OL,18,Fcase more than 600 migrants were on
OL,19,Fboard the boats, the NCA said.
