OL,6,FEbid helped with at least seven
OL,7,Fseparate crossings which carried 3,781
OL,8,Fpeople into Italian waters.
OL,10,FEach migrant had been charged an
OL,11,Faverage of around #3,200, netting
OL,12,Fthose involved #12.3 million, the NCA
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FEbid was detained in Isleworth in June
OL,16,F2023 after the NCA, along with the
OL,17,FItalian Guardia di Finanza and the
OL,18,FItalian coastguard, linked him to the
OL,19,Fcrossings.
