OL,6,FOn a phone seized from him,
OL,7,Finvestigators found pictures of boats,
OL,8,Fconversations about the possible
OL,9,Fpurchase of vessels, videos of
OL,10,Fmigrants making the journey, and
OL,11,Fscreenshots of money transfers.
OL,13,FTim Burton, specialist prosecutor for
OL,14,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service, said:
OL,15,F"Ahmed Ebid played a leading role in a
OL,16,Fsophisticated operation, which
OL,17,Fbreached immigration laws and
OL,18,Fendangered lives, for his own and
OL,19,Fothers' financial gain.
