OL,6,F"Vulnerable people were transported on
OL,7,Flong sea journeys in ill-equipped
OL,8,Ffishing vessels completely unsuitable
OL,9,Ffor carrying the large number of
OL,10,Fpassengers who were on board.
OL,12,F"His repeated involvement in helping
OL,13,Fto facilitate these dangerous
OL,14,Fcrossings showed a complete disregard
OL,15,Ffor the safety of thousands of people,
OL,16,Fwhose lives were put at serious risk."
