OL,6,FJacque Beer, of the NCA, said: "Ebid
OL,7,Fwas part of a crime network who preyed
OL,8,Fupon the desperation of migrants to
OL,9,Fship them across the Mediterranean in
OL,10,Fdeath-trap boats.
OL,12,F"The cruel nature of his business was
OL,13,Fdemonstrated by the callous way he
OL,14,Fspoke of throwing migrants into the
OL,15,Fsea if they didn't follow his rules.
OL,17,F"To him they were just a source of
OL,18,Fprofit.
OL,20,F"He was based in the UK but organising
OL,21,Fcrossings from North Africa.
