OL,6,F"A proportion of those he moved to
OL,7,FItaly would also have ended up in
OL,8,Fnorthern Europe, attempting to cross
OL,9,Fthe Channel to the UK."
OL,11,FHome Office minister Dame Angela Eagle
OL,12,Fsaid: "For too long our borders have
OL,13,Fbeen undermined by vile people-
OL,14,Fsmuggling gangs putting lives at risk
OL,15,Ffor cash.
OL,17,F"Ebid and his associates preyed on
OL,18,Fvulnerable individuals, with hundreds
OL,19,Fbeing crammed on to dangerous boats
OL,20,Fand charged an extortionate fee for
OL,21,Ftheir transport."
